{"tid":2409235,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"用戶個資恐被中國竊取？ Clubhouse：將進行安全更新","createTime":"2021-02-15T15:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T17:44:02.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b48756fd2be853f1e18d81265d9aba7ae2f80b61","tid":2409235,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"目前爆紅的社交軟體Clubhouse，深受很多藝人名流喜愛，連特斯拉創辦人馬斯克也會用。不過，「史丹佛大學網路觀測計劃（SIO）12日發布研究報告，指出Clubhouse存在安全漏洞，讓中國政府有可取得用戶資料的機會。Clubhouse也表示，3日內將進行軟體更新，強化數據安全，包括額外加密及封鎖。<br />\n <br />\nClubhouse與中國的關係先前就有相關爆料，其即時語音聊天技術技術是基於中國公司聲網（Agora）研發，根據《中華人民共和國國家情報法》規定，中國全體須協助情報蒐集，Clubhouse要求使用者在註冊時提供手機號碼，並授權軟體開發商能檢視該使用者通訊錄上聯絡人列表，這意味著使用者的所有聯繫人都被記錄並儲存在開發商伺服器上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-14/536676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-02-14%2F536676&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=90a31684\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-14/536676</a>"},{"pid":"daf51937c312f9b32cbc4b691a73c0ce13c72b82","tid":2409235,"uid":367769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0a3f14a28faa6eec92f3c5232343307af00f17","tid":2409235,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偷曬先嚟更新有鬼用咩"}]}